I like this new series of Power Rangers especially the way the new rangers are introduced and get their gems used for their powers.  Also one of the rangers is a caveman and is proof that the gems stop the aging process of the person who holds it and that each and every ranger has the same ability.  Each ranger has unique things that they bring to the team and help fight the new evil villain Sledge and his minions.  These episodes are the beginning of the team working together and getting to know each other through fighting together and working at the Dino Caf.  This video is for anyone who likes Power Rangers and wants to add to their collection.

Horrible language. 10 mins into the movie and already I hear "pathetic" and "stupid". Is it really necessary? Should have stuck with the Megaforce series which is much more appropriate for children. Sassy attitude between cast members. I can live without burping and bickering as well.
